{"total":62,"pageSize":12,"pageCount":6,"data":[{"title":"浅析JS前端逆向","uid":"d000c68c0537d4a38f7fe3b7716c4e6d","slug":"浅析JS前端逆向","date":"2023-11-28T16:20:30.000Z","updated":"2024-02-14T08:09:01.033Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/浅析JS前端逆向.json","cover":"https://quan9i.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/202303141525110.png","text":"声明文章首发于合天网安实验室https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/uwjSWtItFn2_Wfi570ThlQ 前言js逆向一直没有相关了解，虽然目前渗透遇见的不是很多，大多数遇见的要么不加密，要么无法实现其加密流程，不过最近看到了一个较为简单的站点正好能够逆向出...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"6.8k","symbolsTime":"6 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"前端逆向","slug":"前端逆向","count":1,"path":"api/categories/前端逆向.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"JS","slug":"JS","count":1,"path":"api/tags/JS.json"}],"author":{"name":"quan9i","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://quan9i.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/202303140010598.jpeg","link":"/","description":"国家一级保护废物","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/quan9i","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"https://blog.csdn.net/Reme_mber","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"feature":true},{"title":"内网渗透 | Kerberos协议及其部分攻击手法","uid":"72bf6b540e0d547f829840c591e595f8","slug":"Kerberos协议浅析","date":"2023-11-21T13:19:34.000Z","updated":"2024-02-14T08:24:00.717Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Kerberos协议浅析.json","cover":"https://quan9i.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/202402141623710.jpeg","text":"文章首发于Freebuf社区https://www.freebuf.com/articles/network/384457.html。在内网渗透中，域一直是一个关键角色，在现实情况中，如果能够获得域控的权限，便可以接管域内所有机器。而在域渗透中，Kerberos是最常用的，是整个域的基础认证协议，这里首先简单的介绍Kerberos协议及其部分攻击方式。","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"162k","symbolsTime":"2:27"},"categories":[{"name":"内网","slug":"内网","count":12,"path":"api/categories/内网.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"内网","slug":"内网","count":13,"path":"api/tags/内网.json"}],"author":{"name":"quan9i","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://quan9i.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/202303140010598.jpeg","link":"/","description":"国家一级保护废物","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/quan9i","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"https://blog.csdn.net/Reme_mber","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"feature":true},{"title":"内网渗透|横向常见利用手法","uid":"0e9d1bb6e46bb7063621fff9492a0f83","slug":"内网横向","date":"2023-11-13T06:08:34.000Z","updated":"2024-02-14T08:24:35.133Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/内网横向.json","cover":"https://quan9i.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/202402141615592.jpeg","text":"文章首发于Freebuf社区https://www.freebuf.com/articles/network/382754.html。Windows系统中的网络共享功能可以实现局域网之间的文件共享。通过提供有效的用户凭据，用户可以轻松地将文件从一台机器传输到另一台机器。执行`net share`指令，获得Windows系统默认开启的网络共享","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"186k","symbolsTime":"2:49"},"categories":[{"name":"内网","slug":"内网","count":12,"path":"api/categories/内网.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"内网","slug":"内网","count":13,"path":"api/tags/内网.json"}],"author":{"name":"quan9i","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://quan9i.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/202303140010598.jpeg","link":"/","description":"国家一级保护废物","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/quan9i","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"https://blog.csdn.net/Reme_mber","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"feature":true},{"title":"内网渗透|如何进行权限维持","uid":"b8ca4164abfc3f460c8a00c924b548fd","slug":"内网权限维持","date":"2023-11-09T06:08:34.000Z","updated":"2024-02-14T08:24:54.620Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/内网权限维持.json","cover":"https://quan9i.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/202402141617610.png","text":"文章首发于Freebuf社区https://www.freebuf.com/articles/network/383331.html。在我们成功获取权限后，为了防止管理员发现异常和修复漏洞而导致内网权限丢失，我们往往需要采取一些手段来实现对目标服务器的持久化访问，本文简单介绍权限维持的常见方法","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"235k","symbolsTime":"3:34"},"categories":[{"name":"内网","slug":"内网","count":12,"path":"api/categories/内网.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"内网","slug":"内网","count":13,"path":"api/tags/内网.json"}],"author":{"name":"quan9i","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://quan9i.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/202303140010598.jpeg","link":"/","description":"国家一级保护废物","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/quan9i","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"https://blog.csdn.net/Reme_mber","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"feature":true},{"title":"内网渗透|如何在内网中提升权限","uid":"c2243dfcc1e92746688885810a35d9e9","slug":"内网权限提升","date":"2023-10-18T13:30:34.000Z","updated":"2024-02-14T08:34:43.937Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/内网权限提升.json","cover":"https://quan9i.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/202402141620186.png","text":"文章首发于Freebuf社区https://www.freebuf.com/articles/web/381088.html。在进入内网后，我们如果没有一个较高的权限，有很多命令是无法进行运行的，所以我们在开始内网漫游之前，提权是我们所必须要做的一个东西，这篇文章简单的讲述提权相关的知识","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"121k","symbolsTime":"1:50"},"categories":[{"name":"内网","slug":"内网","count":12,"path":"api/categories/内网.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"内网","slug":"内网","count":13,"path":"api/tags/内网.json"}],"author":{"name":"quan9i","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://quan9i.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/202303140010598.jpeg","link":"/","description":"国家一级保护废物","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/quan9i","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"https://blog.csdn.net/Reme_mber","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"feature":true},{"title":"内网渗透|内网隐藏隧道搭建","uid":"002712540e7d62913692626e59866a05","slug":"内网隐藏隧道搭建","date":"2023-10-10T14:30:34.000Z","updated":"2024-02-14T08:13:41.050Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/内网隐藏隧道搭建.json","cover":"https://quan9i.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/202402141613341.png","text":"文章首发于Freebuf社区https://www.freebuf.com/articles/network/380198.html。在我们获取外网Webshell后，我们想要深入内网，这时候该怎么做呢？如果我们获取的外网webshell具有双网卡，即一张是外网IP，一张是内网IP，我们此时就可以通过搭建隧道来实现在攻击机上访问内网资源，从而进行内网漫游。简单的说也就是隧道是内网的通信证，只有拥有隧道，我们才有资格进入内网漫游。搭建内网隧道一般利用的有三层，应用层，传输层，网络层，接下来依次进行介绍。","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"140k","symbolsTime":"2:08"},"categories":[{"name":"内网","slug":"内网","cou